    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but therapy doesnt change the fact that i've nothing left. no energy, no purpose, nothing. it's like i've already died, i'm just walking around. honestly sometimes it feels like the most logical thing to do is just stop fighting. like, why keep trying to fix something that's already broken?",
